<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">全力保障夏季高峰供水 <strong></strong></span></p>
<p><iframe allowfullscreen="" src="https://v.qq.com/iframe/preview.html?width=500&amp;height=375&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=k3139mpml6y"></iframe></p>
